00:29:39.140 --> 00:29:42.970
pathology approach than we had using a single genomic feature from the

503
00:29:43.040 --> 00:29:43.360
tumor

504
00:29:44.820 --> 00:29:48.360
as I showed previously. And so this, to us, gave us some initial

