00:29:48.400 --> 00:29:51.980
clues that perhaps there was ways to revisit old

506
00:29:51.990 --> 00:29:52.580
datasets,

507
00:29:53.800 --> 00:29:57.690
convert them into high-dimensional pieces of information, but then still

